# Spotify API

- Centralize HTTP in `src/services/spotifyApi.ts`; keep response shapes in `src/services/apiTypes/`.
- Read credentials from `import.meta.env.VITE_SPOTIFY_*` (see `.env.example`).
- OAuth: PKCE for SPA; store tokens in memory or `sessionStorage`, not `localStorage` if avoidable.
- Library save scopes: `user-library-modify`, `user-follow-modify` (see `spotifyAuth.ts`, `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md`).
- Never log access tokens or client secrets.
- Type search/album/track payloads; map API fields to app models in one place.

```typescript
